name: Nasi Kajeng

review 1: One of the best nasi campur in Bangli. I am highly recommended to try this place. This is one of my favorite in Bangli. The Ibu is also very nice, service is great. Sate lilit is also tasty.
review 2: It's just a traditional balinese food store. It's acctualy a local house of balinese people which is set up becoming a store. We can eat in Balinese peaople building, enjoying food made by pork. Yes, it is consist of pork
review 3: This a right place to find a set of balinese spicy cuisine. Rather expensive but still worth for the set delicious pork cuisines.
review 4: Traditional delicious food. Portion was good. We got nasi campur with pork satay.
review 5: Traditional,food is good.Space is family-like. If sate is not hot ask to re-heat

name: Asrama Diklat RSJ Provinsi Bali
address: No. Bangli, Jl. Kesumayudha No.29, Kawan, Kec. Bangli, Kabupaten Bangli, Bali 80613, Indonesia
review 1: Good facilities for students & doctors to stay. Quiet enviroment and comfortable room conditions. Would suggest to buy your dinner before 8pm as you will have to get your dinner outside the RSJ and most places here close by 8pm, latest by 9pm. You will find Indomaret & Alfamart that open for 24hr (about 500m from RSJ).
review 2: This is not a hotel. This is dorm for med student that doing practice training at Bali Mental Hospital
review 3: Nice place to stay spacius and the best central city
